57913::$$$message_0516_0000_0000$$$::I think Illya and I chatted for about an hour.[lr]::
57914::$$$message_0516_0000_0001$$$::Illya happily listened as I talked about meaningless topics and everyday stuff.::
57915::$$$message_0516_0001_0000$$$::...At some point, I realized how heartbreaking this was.[lr]::
57916::$$$message_0516_0001_0001$$$::Illya really is an innocent little girl.[lr]::
57917::$$$message_0516_0001_0002$$$::She doesn't hesitate when it comes to being a Master.[lr]::
57918::$$$message_0516_0001_0003$$$::It's so tragic that she doesn't feel any fear about fighting in a war.::
57919::$$$message_0516_0002_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
57920::$$$message_0516_0002_0001$$$::The magical lineage known as the Einzberns.[lr]::
57921::$$$message_0516_0002_0002$$$::This young girl is who they sent to carry out their thousand-year-old obsession.::
57922::$$$message_0516_0003_0000$$$::If that's Illya's objective too, then I...[lr]::
57923::$$$message_0516_0003_0001$$$::"...Illya. Can I ask you something?"[lr]::
57924::$$$message_0516_0003_0002$$$::"Hm? What?"[lr]::
57925::$$$message_0516_0003_0003$$$::"Does the name Kiritsugu Emiya ring a bell?"[lr]::
57926::$$$message_0516_0003_0004$$$::I just have to know.::
57927::$$$message_0516_0004_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
57928::$$$message_0516_0004_0001$$$::Time stops.[lr]::
57929::$$$message_0516_0004_0002$$$::It's an emotionless silence that seems to erase all the time we've spent together so far.::
57930::$$$message_0516_0005_0000$$$::"No. I don't know anyone like that."[lr]::
57931::$$$message_0516_0005_0001$$$::...Her silver hair sways.[lr]::
57932::$$$message_0516_0005_0002$$$::Illya stands up from the bench and does a little twirl, like a fairy.::
57933::$$$message_0516_0006_0000$$$::"It's almost sunset. Berserker will wake up once it's nighttime, so I should go home."[lr]::
57934::$$$message_0516_0006_0001$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
57935::$$$message_0516_0006_0002$$$::Illya bids me farewell in her childish way.::
57936::$$$message_0516_0007_0000$$$::"Yeah. I better get home, too."[lr]::
57937::$$$message_0516_0007_0001$$$::I stand up from the bench.[lr]::
57938::$$$message_0516_0007_0002$$$::Break time is over.[lr]::
57939::$$$message_0516_0007_0003$$$::The sun's setting, so we're back to being enemies.::
57940::$$$message_0516_0008_0000$$$::And yet, I...[lr]::
57941::$$$message_0516_0008_0001$$$::"Will we meet again, Illya?"[lr]::
57942::$$$message_0516_0008_0002$$$::The question comes naturally to my lips.::
57943::$$$message_0516_0009_0000$$$::"U-um, I'm not sure. I don't think so. Do you want to see me again, Shirou?"[lr]::
57944::$$$message_0516_0009_0001$$$::"Yeah. I wouldn't ask unless I wanted to."[lr]::
57945::$$$message_0516_0009_0002$$$::"Okay! Then I'll come find you tomorrow if I'm in the mood. Don't wait for me, though."[lr]::
57946::$$$message_0516_0009_0003$$$::She runs out of the park.::
57947::$$$message_0516_0010_0000$$$::But...[lr]::
57948::$$$message_0516_0010_0001$$$::The pale girl stops awkwardly.::
57949::$$$message_0516_0011_0000$$$::"I lied earlier. I do know him."::
57950::$$$message_0516_0012_0000$$$::"Illya...?"[lr]::
57951::$$$message_0516_0012_0001$$$::"...I was born to win the Holy Grail War, but my goal is to kill you and Kiritsugu."::
57952::$$$message_0516_0013_0000$$$::Her footsteps fade into the evening.[lr]::
57953::$$$message_0516_0013_0001$$$::Leaving me with that, she leaves without looking back,[lr]::
57954::$$$message_0516_0013_0002$$$::and I watch her go.ïEF